3.2 Mapping

DefaultAssay(RFP) <- "SCT"
DefaultAssay(HB13hpf) <- "SCT"
anchors <- FindTransferAnchors(
  reference = HB13hpf,
  query = RFP,
  k.filter = NA,
  #recompute.residuals = FALSE,
  reference.reduction = "spca",
  normalization.method = "SCT",
  dims = 1:50
  )
